      <branch>
	<branchtitle>The Crucible</branchtitle>
	<branchdescription>
	  <p>
	    In a word, I was too cowardly to do what I knew to be right, as I had been too cowardly
	    to avoid doing what I knew to be wrong.      
	  </p>
	</branchdescription>
